A11yPermission.checkBoxText: Kɔ tẽẽ kɔ ma ho kwan wɔ ɔsram fã mu na ɛnkyerɛ mfɛnsere yi bio .
A11yPermission.content: Saa dwumadie yi hwehwɛ sɛ wɔma dwumadie ho tumi krataa. Sɛ wopɛ sɛ woma ho kwan a, yɛsrɛ wo klik [OK] so. Sɛ wopɛ sɛ wogyae a, yɛsrɛ wo klik [twa] so.
A11yPermission.title: Tumi krataa ho akwammisa krataa .
